snippet.textDisplay:
Honestly if i would have found this 1-2 years ago i would never had gone to full custom loop.

I mean i love it, i spend more time modding it then working/playing, i love to run everything dead silet etc... but initially i wanted to cool the gpu and the only thing i could find was 200€ alphacool or NXZT stuff for aio/bundle GPU or something like G12 kraken bracket + problems with AIO adaptation etc... and the tought was spending 200€ for having half solution and half performance and not long time support, nah let's get into custom loop world.

If i had something like this at 150-160€ to cool both gpu and cpu maybe i would never get into Watercooling. My wallet would be heavier but i would have one less hobby cx
